      "source": [
        "import urllib.request\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import os\n",
        "\n",
        "FILE = \"GSE42296_series_matrix.txt\"\n",
        "URL = \"https://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/geo/series/GSE42nnn/GSE42296/matrix/GSE42296_series_matrix.txt.gz\"\n",
        "\n",
        "if not os.path.exists(FILE):\n",
        "    print(\"Downloading GEO dataset...\")\n",
        "    urllib.request.urlretrieve(URL, FILE + \".gz\")\n",
        "\n",
        "    import gzip, shutil\n",
        "    with gzip.open(FILE + \".gz\", \"rb\") as f_in:\n",
        "        with open(FILE, \"wb\") as f_out:\n",
        "            shutil.copyfileobj(f_in, f_out)\n",
        "\n",
        "data = pd.read_csv(FILE, sep=\"\\t\", comment=\"!\", index_col=0)\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"DATA SHAPE:\", data.shape)\n"
      ],

        "import gzip\n",
        "\n",
        "!wget -q -O GPL6244.annot.gz https://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/geo/platforms/GPL6nnn/GPL6244/annot/GPL6244.annot.gz\n",
        "\n",
        "start = None\n",
        "with gzip.open(\"GPL6244.annot.gz\", \"rt\", errors=\"ignore\") as f:\n",
        "    for i, line in enumerate(f):\n",
        "        if line.startswith(\"ID\\t\"):\n",
        "            start = i\n",
        "            print(\"FOUND HEADER AT LINE:\", start)\n",
        "            print(\"HEADER:\", line[:120])\n",
        "            break\n",
        "\n",
        "annotation = pd.read_csv(\n",
        "    \"GPL6244.annot.gz\",\n",
        "    sep=\"\\t\",\n",
        "    compression=\"gzip\",\n",
        "    skiprows=start,\n",
        "    engine=\"python\",\n",
        "    on_bad_lines=\"skip\"\n",
        ")\n",
        "annotation.columns = [c.strip() for c in annotation.columns]\n",
        "annotation.head()\n"
      ],

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# יצירת meta (time/response) מהקובץ של ה-series matrix\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "\n",
        "matrix_file = FILE  # אם FILE מוגדר אצלך; אם לא, שימי כאן את שם הקובץ כמו: \"GSE42296_series_matrix.txt\"\n",
        "\n",
        "chars_lines = []\n",
        "with open(matrix_file, \"r\", errors=\"ignore\") as f:\n",
        "    for line in f:\n",
        "        if line.startswith(\"!Sample_characteristics_ch1\"):\n",
        "            chars_lines.append(line.strip())\n",
        "\n",
        "time_line = next((l for l in chars_lines if \"\\ttime:\" in l), None)\n",
        "resp_line = next((l for l in chars_lines if \"\\tresponse:\" in l), None)\n",
        "\n",
        "def parse_values(line):\n",
        "    parts = line.split(\"\\t\")[1:]\n",
        "    return [p.strip().strip('\"') for p in parts]\n",
        "\n",
        "time_vals = parse_values(time_line)\n",
        "resp_vals = parse_values(resp_line)\n",
        "\n",
        "meta = pd.DataFrame(index=expr.index)\n",
        "meta[\"time\"] = [\"before\" if \"week 0\" in v else \"after\" for v in time_vals]\n",
        "meta[\"response\"] = [1 if \"R - responder\" in v else 0 for v in resp_vals]\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"meta shape:\", meta.shape)\n",
        "print(\"\\ntime counts:\\n\", meta[\"time\"].value_counts())\n",
        "print(\"\\nresponse counts:\\n\", meta[\"response\"].value_counts())\n",
        "meta.head()\n"
      ],

        "from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split\n",
        "from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestClassifier\n",
        "from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score, roc_auc_score\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "\n",
        "# ניקוי ערכים\n",
        "X = X.apply(pd.to_numeric, errors=\"coerce\")\n",
        "X = X.fillna(X.median())\n",
        "\n",
        "# חלוקה ל-train/test\n",
        "X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(\n",
        "    X, y,\n",
        "    test_size=0.25,\n",
        "    random_state=42,\n",
        "    stratify=y\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "model = RandomForestClassifier(\n",
        "    n_estimators=500,\n",
        "    random_state=42,\n",
        "    class_weight=\"balanced\",\n",
        "    n_jobs=-1\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "model.fit(X_train, y_train)\n",
        "\n",
        "pred = model.predict(X_test)\n",
        "proba = model.predict_proba(X_test)[:, 1]\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"Accuracy:\", accuracy_score(y_test, pred))\n",
        "print(\"ROC AUC:\", roc_auc_score(y_test, proba))\n"
